{"tid":579631,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"另一半同屋企人有衝突會點處理?","createTime":"2018-03-03T18:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T19:09:10.000Z","uid":33632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"131cd44d54df8980fd241bc80ee8d7cf702b86aa","tid":579631,"uid":33632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:43:58.000Z","msg":"各位既另一半如果係你面前同佢屋企人嘈交，大家會點處理？<br />\n<br />\n講下自己先，我試過係女朋友屋企既時侯女朋友同佢啊媽／家姐嘈，我都唔知可以點，咪唔出聲<br />\n<br />\n氣氛又尷尬，但佢地越講越嬲　女朋友就問我係咪佢啊媽／家姐唔岩　係佢地面前我都唔知點答<br />\n<br />\n幫邊一邊都死　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲分享下<br />\n<br />\n或者點處理好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　"},{"pid":"23d32cc89d3a008a19ff50e5c1f41f750562c566","tid":579631,"uid":53794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:45:52.000Z","msg":"冷靜啲 其實件事仲有好多睇法嘅...<br />\n之後帶佢地遊花園 然後你就會俾兩邊一齊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6abb4ada7ee8a39849fbccc81e5683ff3d3888","tid":579631,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:45:56.000Z","msg":"你自己諗食條女定人地啊媽"},{"pid":"0e7d15ab8655f1897d336e111e9a1ea63f7e0d6d","tid":579631,"uid":174074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:47:36.000Z","msg":"最好保持中立 始終人地先係有血緣關係<br />\n到時是但一方冇事 就會同對方講你撐邊邊個<br />\n你都唔想第日面左左"},{"pid":"445564b309921005d2316eb3b2b61cfcb4bec422","tid":579631,"uid":33632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e7d15ab8655f1897d336e111e9a1ea63f7e0d6d","tid":579631,"uid":174074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:47:36.000Z","msg":"最好保持中立 始終人地先係有血緣關係<br />\n到時是但一方冇事 就會同對方講你撐邊邊個<br />\n你都唔想第日面左左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:56:38.000Z","msg":"我都想中立　中立係女友眼中＝我唔幫佢<br />\n<br />\n嬲埋我就死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　打好關係真係唔容易"},{"pid":"abe701925806